Package fr.cs.Group07.myVelib

Class UserBalance

java.lang.Object
fr.cs.Group07.myVelib.UserBalance
public class UserBalance extends Object
The UserBalance class represents the balance of a user, including the number of rides, total rent time, total charges, and time-credit earned.
